Organizers' Collaborative is a Boston-based organization established in 1999 to '''promote better use of technology by social change organizations''' throughout the US.

The Organizers' Collaborative is dedicated to advancing social change through the effective use of technology. We are particularly committed to low-cost and no-cost tools created in the spirit of Open Source. 

URL = http://organizerscollaborative.org/


